item.title: About Me
item.description: At Ginzan Onsen I was born February 5th, 1995. I got my bachelor’s degree in Computer Science from the University of Puerto Rico at Río Piedras in early 2018. Apart from computer science and math, I enjoy studying philosophy and different languages. If you’re interested in my resume, you can obtain it here.

item.title: Open Source Projects
item.description: Here are my open-source projects as well as some projects I’ve contributed to. noticias-pr A command-line interface for reading the latest from local news sites in Puerto Rico. Tech Highlights: NodeJS Web scraping Available on npm cc-api An open-source API for Caribbean Cinemas. Tech Highlights: TypeScript MongoDB Web scraping Available at: http://cc.rauln.com TypeDoc available at: https://raulnegron.me/cc-api/ django-athm Django app for handling ATH Móvil payments.
